    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="subheader-color gary-yellow ben-border">
      <div class="subheader">
        <div class="logoContainer">
          <Image
            id="GLogoImage"
            class="logoImage"
            src={GLogo}
            alt="No Dialogue"
          />
        </div>
        <p>
          Gary the Duck is a music video I directed and animated for Greg Blum.
          I animated the characters in Adobe Animate - lineart by Greg Blum,
